<div class="container py-4">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
      <h1>About Rise and Resound</h1>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x300/6c757d/ffffff?text=Rise+and+Resound+Story"
             alt="About Rise and Resound" class="img-fluid rounded">
      </div>

      <div class="lead mb-4">
        Founded in Winnipeg, Manitoba in 2022, Rise and Resound is a solo-run motivational brand with a mission to empower individuals through storytelling, personal development, and resilience training.
      </div>

      <h3>Our Story</h3>
      <p>Rise and Resound began as a passion project focused on sharing stories of resilience and personal growth. What started as small speaking engagements at local schools has grown into a comprehensive platform for motivation and personal development.</p>

      <p>We believe that everyone has a story worth telling and the potential to overcome any challenge. Through our speaking engagements, digital products, and coaching services, we help individuals discover their inner strength and develop the resilience needed to thrive.</p>

      <h3>What We Offer</h3>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h5>Speaking Engagements</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>School assemblies and student programs</li>
            <li>Corporate workshops and team building</li>
            <li>Youth development events</li>
            <li>Conference keynote presentations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h5>Digital Products</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Motivational eBooks and guides</li>
            <li>Daily affirmation packages</li>
            <li>Pre-recorded speech collections</li>
            <li>Personal development resources</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Our Mission</h3>
      <p>To empower individuals through storytelling, personal development, and resilience training. We are committed to helping people discover their potential, overcome challenges, and create positive change in their lives and communities.</p>

      <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <%= link_to "Book a Speaking Engagement", new_booking_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg me-3" %>
        <%= link_to "Browse Products", products_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
